name: Timeless Tabbies: A Feline History Tour

metadata.name: Neo-Neko: The Cyberpunk City Cat
metadata.description: Introducing Neo-Neko, the cyberpunk city cat. This sleek and sophisticated robotic feline is the perfect companion for navigating the neon-lit streets of a futuristic metropolis. With its advanced artificial intelligence, Neo-Neko is able to adapt to any situation and provide valuable assistance to its owner. Whether it's keeping watch while you sleep, serving as a messenger between you and your cyberpunk crew, or just providing some much-needed companionship in a lonely, high-tech world, Neo-Neko is always ready to lend a helping paw. With its durable, weather-proof exterior and customizable LED lighting, Neo-Neko is the ultimate accessory for any cyberpunk aficionado.
